<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>I’m delighted to announce that we’ve just released <a href="http://www.springsource.org/roo">Spring Roo</a> 1.1.0.M1. Spring Roo is the fastest way for Java developers to build Spring-based applications in the Java programming language. With the Roo 1.1.0.M1 you can build working web applications - complete with a <a href="https://code.google.com/webtoolkit/">Google Web Toolkit</a> (GWT) front end - in as little as 200 keystrokes! Plus as usual we’ve concurrently released a new version of <a href="http://www.springsource.com/products/springsource-google-download">SpringSource Tool Suite</a> (STS 2.3.3.M1) which is optimised for the latest and greatest Roo goodies!</p>
<p>There are over <a href="https://jira.springsource.org/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10340&amp;version=11238">200 fixes, enhancements and new features</a> since our 1.0.2 release three months ago. Some of the highlights include:</p>
